statements: SELECT * FROM inventory
SELECT item_name, quantity FROM inventory ORDER BY quantity DESC
SELECT location, price FROM inventory WHERE quantity > 10
SELECT id, item_name, price FROM inventory WHERE item_name LIKE 'A%'
SELECT * FROM inventory WHERE price BETWEEN 50.00 AND 100.00
SELECT id, item_name, quantity FROM inventory WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY item_name DESC, quantity ASC
SELECT * FROM inventory WHERE location = 'Warehouse A' AND quantity > 10 ORDER BY price ASC
SELECT item_name, location FROM inventory WHERE quantity BETWEEN 5 AND 20 ORDER BY location ASC, item_name DESC
SELECT id, price FROM inventory WHERE item_name LIKE '%apple%' OR item_name LIKE '%banana%' ORDER BY price DESC
SELECT item_name, quantity, price FROM inventory WHERE location IN ('Store A', 'Store B') ORDER BY quantity DESC, price ASC
SELECT * FROM medical_equipment;
SELECT equipment_name, quantity FROM medical_equipment WHERE equipment_id = 1;
SELECT supply_name, quantity FROM supplies ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT equipment_name, quantity FROM medical_equipment WHERE quantity > 5;
SELECT * FROM supplies WHERE quantity < 10;
SELECT equipment_id, equipment_name, quantity FROM medical_equipment WHERE equipment_id > 100 ORDER BY equipment_name DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM supplies WHERE quantity < 50 ORDER BY supply_name ASC
SELECT equipment_name, quantity FROM medical_equipment WHERE quantity BETWEEN 10 AND 20
SELECT equipment_id, equipment_name FROM medical_equipment WHERE equipment_name LIKE 'S%'
SELECT supply_name, quantity FROM supplies ORDER BY quantity DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM Inventory;
SELECT name, quantity, price FROM Inventory ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT id, name, quantity FROM Inventory WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT * FROM Suppliers WHERE contact_name LIKE 'J%';
SELECT id, name, order_date FROM Orders WHERE order_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Inventory ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT name, quantity, price FROM Inventory WHERE quantity > 50 AND price <= 100.00;
SELECT i.name, s.name AS supplier_name, o.quantity AS ordered_quantity FROM Inventory i INNER JOIN Orders o ON i.id = o.item_id LEFT JOIN Suppliers s ON o.supplier_id = s.id;
SELECT i.name, SUM(o.quantity) AS total_ordered_quantity FROM Inventory i INNER JOIN Orders o ON i.id = o.item_id GROUP BY i.name;
SELECT i.name, o.order_date FROM Inventory i JOIN Orders o ON i.id = o.item_id WHERE o.order_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM medical_equipments;
SELECT id, name, category FROM medical_equipments WHERE quantity > 0;
SELECT supplier_id, SUM(quantity_change) AS total_quantity_change FROM inventory_log GROUP BY supplier_id;
SELECT * FROM suppliers WHERE location LIKE 'New%';
SELECT patient_id, doctor_id, consultation_date FROM telehealth_consultations ORDER BY consultation_date DESC;
SELECT name, category, quantity FROM medical_equipments ORDER BY name DESC;

SELECT suppliers.name, suppliers.location, COUNT(inventory_log.id) AS log_count FROM suppliers LEFT JOIN inventory_log ON suppliers.id = inventory_log.supplier_id GROUP BY suppliers.name, suppliers.location;

SELECT medical_equipments.name, suppliers.name AS supplier, inventory_log.quantity_change FROM medical_equipments INNER JOIN inventory_log ON medical_equipments.id = inventory_log.equipment_id INNER JOIN suppliers ON inventory_log.supplier_id = suppliers.id WHERE inventory_log.quantity_change > 0;

SELECT telehealth_consultations.consultation_date, suppliers.name AS supplier, suppliers.location FROM telehealth_consultations LEFT JOIN inventory_log ON telehealth_consultations.id = inventory_log.equipment_id INNER JOIN suppliers ON inventory_log.supplier_id = suppliers.id WHERE suppliers.location = 'New York';

SELECT DISTINCT medical_equipments.category, COUNT(inventory_log.id) AS log_count FROM medical_equipments INNER JOIN inventory_log ON medical_equipments.id = inventory_log.equipment_id GROUP BY medical_equipments.category HAVING log_count > 5 ORDER BY log_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM medical_equipment;
SELECT item_name, unit_price FROM medical_equipment ORDER BY unit_price DESC;
SELECT patient_name, consultation_date FROM telehealth_consultations WHERE consultation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT supplier_name, address FROM equipment_suppliers ORDER BY supplier_name ASC;
SELECT equipment_id, arrival_date, location FROM inventory_tracking WHERE location = 'Warehouse';
SELECT * FROM medical_equipment WHERE unit_price > 1000;
SELECT item_name, quantity FROM medical_equipment WHERE quantity >= 10 ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT e.item_name, t.patient_name, i.location FROM medical_equipment e JOIN inventory_tracking i ON e.id = i.equipment_id JOIN telehealth_consultations t ON t.id = i.id;
SELECT s.supplier_name, o.order_date, e.unit_price FROM equipment_suppliers s JOIN supply_orders o ON s.id = o.id JOIN medical_equipment e ON o.equipment_id = e.id WHERE o.quantity_ordered > 50;
SELECT COUNT(id) AS total_consultations FROM telehealth_consultations WHERE consultation_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
